dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contours, hachures, spot heights, and form lines. Shows cadastral information, township and property boundaries, quarries, overhead H.T. electricity and telegraph lines, post offices, public and private properties. " © United Republic of Tanzania 1968". Includes index diagram to adjoining sheets. Based on aerial photographs. Information on the number of sheet published for covering this area is unavailable. Map Collection has seven.
dc_publisher_s: [Dar es Salaam] : Survey Division, Ministry of Lands Settlement and Water Development, 1968.
